### Create a NPC
# @name create
POST http://localhost:4000/api/npcs/create
content-type: application/json

{
  "type": "goblin",
  "locationId": "fbf9a3d2-52dc-40fc-a3a1-b17874b79c46"
}

### Get new NPC id
@agentId = {{create.response.body.$.entities[0].id}}

### Get NPC  
GET http://localhost:4000/api/npcs/{{agentId}}

### Get ALL NPCs
GET http://localhost:4000/api/npcs

### Damage an NPC
POST http://localhost:4000/api/npcs/{{agentId}}/damage
content-type: application/json

{
  "value": {{$randomInt 2 8}}
}

### Move a NPC somewhere
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/npcs/{{agentId}}/move/b9a19fc6-405f-495d-8e0e-f68d67529ddb
